用态矢相继的相干分解来解释相干叠加结果及其变化。这时沿 $z$ 方向和 $x$ 方向的相干分解分别为
$$
\left\{
\begin{array}{l}
|+z\rangle=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\left(|+x\rangle+|-x\rangle\right) \\
|-z\rangle=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\left(|+x\rangle-|-x\rangle\right)
\end{array}
\right.,
\left\{
\begin{array}{l}
|+x\rangle=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\left(|+z\rangle+|-z\rangle\right) \\
|-x\rangle=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\left(|+z\rangle-|-z\rangle\right)
\end{array}
\right.
$$
分解式中 $\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}$ 系数表示经过 S-G 装置时束流强度守恒。当非极化电子束穿过第一个磁场沿 $z$ 方向的 S-G 装置时，入射束相干分解分成两束：
$$
|\ln\rangle={\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}}\left(|+z\rangle+|-z\rangle\right)
$$
这时如果作记录，表明非相干分解，成为沿 $z$ 方向分布的两个斑点；而不作测量记录时，这两束仍保留相干性。
接着，对于后面情况，向 $\pm z$ 方向飞行的两个分束再经受第二个 S-G 装置的沿 $x$ 方向相干分解，成为
$$
\left\{
\begin{array}{ll}
{\displaystyle {\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}}|+z\rangle={\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}}{\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}}(|+z,+x\rangle+|+z,-x\rangle)} & {\Rightarrow} & {\left\{
\begin{array}{l}
{\displaystyle {\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}}{\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}}|+z,+x\rangle} \\
{\displaystyle {\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}}{\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}}|+z,-x\rangle}
\end{array}
\right.} \\
{\displaystyle {\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}}|-z\rangle={\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}}{\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}}(|-z,+x\rangle-|-z,-x\rangle)} & {\Rightarrow} & {\left\{
\begin{array}{l}
{\displaystyle {\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}}{\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}}|-z,+x\rangle} \\
{\displaystyle {-{\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}}{\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}}|-z,-x\rangle}}
\end{array}
\right.}
\end{array}
\right.
$$
这里，记号 $|+z,+x\rangle$ 表示此束先经由 $+z$ 束再经 $+x$ 束分解而来。这时沿 4 个方向 $(+z,+x),(+z,-x),(-z,+x),(-z,-x)$ 飞行 4 个分束。如果测量记录，将得到 4 个斑点。如不测量记录，则仍保持着相干性。注意这里分解的正负号。
最后，再经受第三个 S-G 装置的沿 $z$ 方向相干分解，成为向如下 8 个方向飞行的 8 个分束：
$$
\begin{array}{c}
{\displaystyle {\overbrace{\sqrt{2}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\left|+z,+x\right\rangle}} \\
{\displaystyle {\overbrace{\sqrt{2}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\left|+z,-x\right\rangle}} \\
{\displaystyle {\overbrace{\sqrt{2}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\left|-z,+x\right\rangle}} \\
{\displaystyle {\overbrace{\sqrt{2}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\left|-z,+x\right\rangle}}
\end{array}
\Leftrightarrow
\left\{
\begin{array}{c}
{\displaystyle {\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\left|+z,+x\right\rangle=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\left(\left|+z,+x,+z\right\rangle+\left|+z,+x\right\rangle\right\rangle}} \\
{\displaystyle {\overbrace{\sqrt{2}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\left|+z,-x\right\rangle=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\left(\left|+z,-x\right\rangle-z\right\rangle-\left|+z,-x\right\rangle\right\rangle}} \\
{\displaystyle {\overbrace{\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\left|-z,+x\right\rangle=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\left|-z,+x\right\rangle=\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\left(\left|-z,+x,+z\right\rangle+\left|-z,+x\right\rangle\right\rangle}} \\
{\displaystyle {\overbrace{-\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\left|-z,-x\right\rangle=-\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\left|-z,-x\right\rangle=-\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}}\left(\left|-z,-x,+z\right\rangle-\left|-z,-z\right\rangle\right\rangle}}
\end{array}
\right.}
$$
现在，如果令第 2 个 S-G 装置中电流逐渐减小，直至为零。相应地，分为两行每行 4 个的最终 8 个斑点相互靠拢，合并成为一行。但上面分解式清楚表明，这一行中间两对 4 个斑点相应于 $\left(\left|+z,+x,-z\right\rangle,\left|+z,-x,-z\right\rangle\right)$ 和 $\left(\left|-z,+x,+z\right\rangle,\left|-z,-x,+z\right\rangle\right)$ 两对，因彼此相位相反，相消干涉而消失。最后只剩下沿 $z$ 方向最外端（对应 $\left(+z,+z\right),\left(-z,-z\right)$）的两个斑点，相当于一个（加强了的）沿 $z$ 方向 S-G 装置起的作用。
在最后一步变化的全过程里，总强度是守恒的。因为 8 个光点的每个振幅为 $\frac{1}{\sqrt{8}}$ 在合并过程中，有
$$
2\left({\frac{1}{\sqrt{8}}}+{\frac{1}{\sqrt{8}}}\right)^{2}=1
$$
